EmailTemplate.subject: Can I Send You a Pair of Rangers Tickets? (1494445744.0)
EmailTemplate.textOnly: ​ Hi Brian, With baseball season underway and summer right around the corner, I want to make sure you have a chance to spend some time cheering on the Rangers in Arlington. Turbonomic is giving away a pair of Rangers tickets to the game of your choice (June- August) for simply scheduling a 30-minute meeting with a Turbonomic engineer during the month of May. Schedule your meeting here <[[http://info.turbonomic.com/Xgg0KjI0Z000HrmxX01aZe0]]>, and we will get you over to Globe Life Park! Best, Catherine Catherine Kellogg Sr. Marketing Program Manager O: 781.418.5280 | M: 617.306.1485 Catherine.kellogg@turbonomic.com <[[http://info.turbonomic.com/WZ0akZImg0f1HgK00X0xr00]]>
